=head1 DESCRIPTION

The configuration for the allowed video and screen sharing capabilities
for participants present over the call. For more information, see Set
up in-app, web, video calling, and screen sharing capabilities
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/connect/latest/adminguide/inapp-calling.html)
in the I<Amazon Connect Administrator Guide>.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 ScreenShare => Str

The screen sharing capability that is enabled for the participant.
C<SEND> indicates the participant can share their screen.


=head2 Video => Str

The configuration having the video and screen sharing capabilities for
participants over the call.



